<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.IDataArray.UpdateCounterResetValue" Title="UpdateCounterResetValue method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IDataArray">IDataArray</PageRef> ->
    UpdateCounterResetValue
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>UpdateCounterResetValue</TypeRef> method modifies the reset value to use for the counter, if the buffer has been created with one attached.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[void UpdateCounterResetValue(uint32_t counterResetValue);]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Argument list">
      <ArgumentList>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="uint32_t" Name="counterResetValue">
          The new value to assign to the attached counter when the counter is reset.
        </ArgumentListEntry>
      </ArgumentList>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="See also">
    <PageRefList>
      <PageRefListEntry PageName="cobalt.graphics.IDataArray">IDataArray</PageRefListEntry>
    </PageRefList>
  </Section>
</XMLDocContent>
